Multimedia artist Chance Watt produces works that pulsate with energy. He evokes movement through both form and colour. A figure emerges from the fiery orange and dark amber background in this piece. Her presence, although striking, is almost a suggestion as her features are so delicately modelled. This concept is crucial to Watt's artworks, which toe the line between illusion and reality. Dark purple and mauve strands intertwine across the subject, almost enveloping her. The artist conveys a sense of movement here, his brushstrokes dancing across the canvas. Watt conjures activity in this piece through his choices of colour palette. As analogous colours, the nature of purple and orange is to compliment yet contrast one another. This dynamic between the two colours brings the work to life, stimulating our minds as we endeavour to digest this work.

The CroSkull Soul Bound Token is a non-transferable non-fungible token (NFT) that represents a person's ownership and participation in the CroSkull's Council decentralized autonomous organization. This token is tied to the owner's digital identity and cannot be transferred or sold to anyone else.  As the owner of a soul-bound token, you will have the opportunity to participate in the governance of the Council by voting on important decisions and proposals.  In addition to participating in Council governance, you will have access to exclusive perks and benefits offered by the organization. Captain’s log. Year 2301. Space. The engines are finally off and I’m using the short time we have before hibernation to record this message for any intelligent life form who might ever listen to it. I’m speaking as a representative of human beings as we fly away from our native planet into the sidereal emptiness; banished by those same species we’ve been greedily exploiting for so long, while we could have simply shared with them the plentiful resources we had. In order not to repeat the same mistakes, the High Council of Human Race has agreed on putting a sophisticated artificial intelligence in charge of the reconstruction of humanity. And now this AI is streaming on every screen of the ship images from the few active cameras left on Earth of our fleets escaping; an eternal memento of why we put it in charge. Time for me to go, there’s a long journey ahead and most probably I’ll end my days on this ship, searching for a planet that might not even exist. What a shame. Over and out.

Captain’s log. Year 3301. Earth’s orbit.  Operation Endless has finally begun, just as scheduled 1000 years ago after Exodus. Spaceships have gathered around our native planet from all over the universe, perfectly synchronized by the guidance of VerAI.  Probes have returned from a first inspection to the planet and the results are unbelievable.  Nature reconquered the whole environment and evolved according to fractal patterns that seem to be dictated by a sentient mind.  If this sounds incredible, just wait for the rest.  We have proof that natural elements have absorbed the memory of humans and reproduced their shape. Grass, rock, sand, metal… Even water preserves in its molecules the shape of human race. This planet was sentenced to death by our ancestors and yet it decided to remember them as if it had a mind of its own.  We are sending out our exploration spaceships and robots ‘cause we might have found a portal to the core of the planet.  Sending updates soon.  Over and out.

They decided to get together as a group and organize protests to raise awareness about its benefits. Their leader was a guy named BigJack.cro, who firmly believed that Cronos blockchain and Crypto.com was the key to a better and fairer future. He was passionate and charismatic, and he managed to gather a determined group of people who shared his views, and thus he created the Cro Cult.  As the months went by, the group grew in numbers and influence, holding larger and more militant demonstrations. Unfortunately, some demonstrations turned violent, with protests ending in rampages. The protesters, under the influence of BigJack, believed that this was the only way to make their voices heard and to pressure the world to adopt Cronos.  Police and local authorities began to take action to quell the violent protests, and many members of the group were arrested. BigJack.cro was charged with inciting violence and was imprisoned. Without their leader, the group continues to thrive, and is trying to pressure the government to release him from prison. So their message of the importance of Cronos continues to be spread by those who have been inspired by their passionate commitment, and it is through a collection of committed NFTs, that the message continues to be spread, and The Cro Cult can spread until the world folds in.

Works often influenced by the events from his personal life or day-to-day reflections about the world around him.
drops.description: This 6 piece collection was created with an intention to admire certain elements important to the creative process, but also life in general. The aim of every one of these six artworks is to make the new owner just take a small break and ponder about one of those topics, as well as admire their influence on the surrounding world. I chose the form factor of a surreal museum-like space, because ever since I was a small child, I thought about modern art galleries as the calm, quiet places designed to let the observer admire and reflect upon the odd, non-conventional and often controversial concepts. I hope that events taking place in this little space I designed in my head will succeed in their goal.

drops.description:
Hello everyone, 

I have always had a passion for art which most already know, but what most donÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t know is that I am very fond of equestrian sports. Growing up I self-taught to become an equestrian rider. I have also judged equestrian events and competitions and organized charity festivals in support of children with disabilities. 

Riding horses can be very healing for children and their psycho-emotional state and for those who become more involved, assists with muscle development. I used to coach children for free but have retired from this. However, I keep in close contact with the equestrian club in my hometown and occasionally still assist by running the group classes for children. I also financially support and support them with media coverage, assisting with fund raising to help kids receive this amazing and free therapy with horses.

To support the equestrian club and children, I am auctioning a limited-edition 1:1 Ã¢â‚¬ËœRare Heart HodlerÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ NFT. It also comes with a T-shirt and an autographed card from myself. drops.description:
Looneycorns is the first of 5 unique toys from the Lost Toy collection. Each toy character represents a childhood favourite that has been lost over time and needs a new home.

Those who look after their toys/NFTs will have the opportunity to receive amazing weekly prizes from our ToyBox and earn tokens. This could be to win a night's stay at the Hilton for two, limited edition trainers, or even sought after NFTs! You, our community, will decide!

In addition, holders of our NFTs will have exclusive access to our platform SnipeHub designed to help manage your ever-growing NFT portfolio with ease and “snipe” better deals!

Finally, at Lost Toys we believe that every child deserves a toy to build memories with and for that reason, we plan to also support those in need with toy donations.

UTILITIES

PLATFORM ACCESS - Exclusive free access to our platform SnipeHub and future applications

TOYBOX REWARDS - Holders will be entered into a weekly raffle, to win IRL rewards

CHARITY DONATIONS - We will be donating toys to the Toy Project charity on a monthly basis

AIRDROPS - Collectors of our NFTs will receive multiple airdrops

DAO - Holders of our airdropped NFTs will be able to vote on the next toys and future SnipeHub platform functionality

NON-MONETIZED TOKENIZATION - Holders will be able to stake our NFTs to earn tokens to make raffle purchases

REAL LIFE TOYS - We will be sending to NFT holders of all 5 toy characters (these will be minted throughout the phases) a real life collectable toy

AUTO WHITELIST TO FUTURE MINTS - Holders of our toys will get discounts on future mints

THE ARTIST

The design of our NFT collection is extremely important to us, as it is often the first thing people see when exploring collections and we wanted people to own something truly special.

For this reason, we have spared no expense and commissioned the services of renowned 3D artist Felipe Rui, whose fame comes from his famous collection of “dark Disney” art designs, which have been presented in in many galleries.

Are you ready for the next generation of NFTs?

Then welcome to CroHamsterNFT.

CroHamsterNFT is an innovative project that tries to achieve maximum utility and innovation for the success of our community and project.

For this we have created a very limited collection that only contains 1000 3D animated and unique CroHamsters with different cosmetic items, weapons and 8 unique animations. 
Each CroHamster also has two special combat values ​​that will be useful to fight other CroHamsters. 

The Crohamsters are divided into 4 different factions (Miner, Space, Nature, Worker) and can fight against each other in the CroHamster-Arena. With this feature, we will be able to start a unique reward system for our community, in which they can win Cro rewards and points on a leaderboard thought fights in the arena. For this, each CroHamster has Attack and Defense combat stats that indicate how strong it is in fights against other CroHamsters. Additionally, if the CroHamster owns a weapon, it will get an attack bonus. To prevent stale and predictable fights, we will also use a random generated "Luck" and "Hit Percentage" value.

Every Crohamster who wants to take part in the arena fights can put their name on a list, two random CroHamsters from different factions are then selected from this list to fight against each other. The winner will then receive the mint price of a CroHamster NFT in Cro as prize (325Cro). They will also earn points on a leaderboard, allowing us to honor the best CroHamster fighters in a Hall of Fame, which qualifies them for additional Hall of Fame giveaways with unique NFT and CRO rewards.

The Rebel AUT Club is a new digital collection that is being launched to provide support to children with autism and their families. The collection will consist of 8 animal-themed NFTs with different attributes and rarities. 

When purchasing one of these unique NFTs, collectors will not only have the opportunity to own a one-of-a-kind piece of digital art, they will also be contributing to a good cause. Making a real impact in the lives of children with autism. 

As you may know, children with autism often have difficulty with sensory processing. This can impact their ability to engage in daily activities and interact with their environment.

Our project is centred around the donation of unique sensory equipment that is essential to the development and growth of vital social, fine, and gross motor skills. Along with the goal of providing support to these children in their daily lives.

Together we can make a difference! We would love for you to be a part of this amazing project and assist us in making a difference for children with ASD in all our communities. 

Thank you for your support!

This is not the end, it's only the beginning.
Pogo holder will be our first priority to benefit them with our future roadmap, partnership, future collection or even cross chain project.

drops.description:
Coom Cats: A Cronos-based project featuring a collection of 1,000 Cats.

Our ambition is to breathe fresh life into the Cronos blockchain and to provide community solutions through the various utilities we plan to implement.

For now, we can share some of these utilities with you (with others remaining confidential):

Step 1 - Presale Platform:
Our platform aims to deliver long-term benefits to COOM token holders. By creating a robust and scalable project, COOM seeks to profit from NFT project presales, taking a percentage fee from the profits and then redistributing a certain percentage of that as passive income to holders weekly. The more Coom Cats NFTs you hold, the greater your passive income potential. Future aspirations for the platform include cross-chain capabilities.

Step 2 - Coom Club:

Benefits of joining the Investor's Club:

Regular Updates on Our Activities: Keeping club members informed about CoomLabs' latest news.

Early Glimpses of Our Future Features: Sneak peeks of upcoming features, with detailed information provided in advance to club members.

Exclusive COOMLABS Industry Offers: Club members can enjoy preferential rates on exclusive merchandising as well as future subscriptions. This offer is reserved exclusively for Investor's Club members for private use.

Dedicated Online Private Space: Access a private area where you can interact with other club members.

Step 3 - CoomLabs:
More information to come.

Step 4 - COOM Platform:
Currently confidential.

Each of our utilities addresses the growing demands of the ecosystem. Our long-term goal is to meet these needs while establishing a project and ecosystem that's scalable in the long run.

drops.description:
BOB Headz is a new, super limited NFT collection from the BOB Adventures ecosystem.

Our main mission for this collection is to grow our community with more and more positive people who like crypto, gaming, passive income and other activities.  If you want to join our community and enjoy different utilities, this is the right place!

UTILITY This collection will unlock our new game - Flappy BOB Game that everyone knows and are easy to play using PC or Mobile. BOB Headz will be used in our game and everyone who holds BOB Headz can play it! We will have online leaderboard where we will track players with best scores every week and we will reward them! But it will be harder than you think! Each NFT will be 1 life. Life resets every 24H, so if you hold 1x BOB Headz NFT, you can play 1 time per 24H. If you hold 10x BOB Headz, you can play 10 times per 24H and so on... The more Headz you own, the better chance to get better score. There also will be burn mechanism - part of secondary sale royalties we will use to sweep BOB Headz floor and burn them. This way we will reduce total supply from time to time. So this collection will be more and more valuable in the future. 

LEGENDARY BOB HEADz In our collection you can find 20 1/1 Legendaries and if you mint one of them, you can claim their bounty!  Each legendary bounty is different, it can be free NFT, crypto coin and more!

 MINTING REWARDS Also there are minting rewards that will be distributed to random minters when 25%, 50%, 75% and 100% is minted! Join our Discord for more info!

The Heroes Gen.0 Collection is a collection of unique and powerful Heroes that will play a crucial role in the gameplay experience of Ebisu's Bay. Each Hero will bring their singular skills in the battlefield, leading your army, get access to Heroes cloning, gather resources and accomplish legendary quests! 

Heroes Gen.0 are the first of their kind, and they have been carefully crafted to be balanced and fair. If you want to be a leader in Ebisu's Bay, then you will need a Hero Gen.0 on your side.
drops.description:
A limited amount of 330 unique and powerful Heroes will be available for mint on Ebisu's Bay today November 2nd, 2023. 

**Mint details**: 
- Available for mint: 330 Heroes Gen.0 
- Time: 8pm UTC 
- Maximum mint per wallet: 20 
- Bids start at 15,000 $FRTN, moving to a lower mint price at each bid, as price will re adjust every 5 minutes. 
- Auction duration: 24 hours

**Note**: Each bid will lower the price for everyone. If you minted at a higher price, you will be able to withdraw the difference. 

**Of all $FRTN spent**: Once minted out and the final price is set, all remaining $FRTN will be burnt except: 
- 0.25% to Ebisu's Owners 
- 0.25% to Felisgarde's Owners 
- 1% to Lighthouses' 
- Owners 1.5% to Inns' Owners 

Proceeds will be deposited to the owner's rewards vault during season 2

Learn more about Heroes on our Wiki: <https://www.notion.so/ebisusbay/Heroes-bf7562f290d947fd8dac095aa9c6f883> 

**Get your Hero Gen.0 today!**

drops.title: Ryoshi Tales: Wooden Wyrm Welcoming
drops.subtitle: Get ready to be part of this extraordinary event. This is your chance to own a piece of digital artistry, celebrate the Year of the Wooden Dragon, and elevate your standing within the Ryoshi Dynasties. Whether you’re drawn to the beauty of the artwork, the unique benefits, or the thrill of the collectible, the Wooden Wyrm Welcoming is an unmissable occasion.
drops.description:
As we usher in the 2024 Chinese New Year, Ebisu’s Bay is proud to present a remarkable event that blends tradition with the modernity of the digital era. The “Wooden Wyrm Welcoming” celebrates the Year of the Wooden Dragon, an emblem of strength, prosperity, and fortune. This exclusive NFT collection consists of 300 meticulously designed pieces, each embodying the spirit of this auspicious year. Mark your calendars for the launch on February 9th at 6 PM UTC, as this event promises to be a cornerstone in the world of digital collectibles.



### **Collection Overview**
- Total Pieces: 300 Unique NFTs
- Theme: Celebrating the Year of the Wooden Dragon
- Launch Date: February 9th at 6 PM UTC
- Special Releases: Two 1:1 NFTs with exceptional benefits

### **Exclusive Benefits and Pricing**
- Standard Price: 1000 FRTN for general holders or when utilizing locked rewards.
- Discounted Price: 700 FRTN for those holding 1000 or more Mitama, rewarding their significant contributions to our ecosystem.
- Minting Policy: Each wallet may mint one NFT every 5 minutes, ensuring equitable access until the collection is sold out.

### **1:1 Releases: Nightfall Keeper and Guardian of First Light**
- Nightfall Keeper: A rare NFT that grants the holder 500 troops when staked in the Barracks, significantly enhancing strategic capabilities in Ryoshi Dynasties.
- Guardian of First Light: The pinnacle of rarity, offering +1% APR when staked in the Bank and an additional 50 troops, thereby augmenting both your earning potential and battle readiness.
- Other common, uncommon and rare NFTs will grant standard rank based seasonal benefits.

### **Why Participate?**
The Wooden Wyrm Welcoming transcends the conventional NFT drop. It is a fusion of cultural heritage and digital innovation. This collection exemplifies the creativity of our community and the vast possibilities within the Ebisu’s Bay ecosystem. Designed to offer both aesthetic appeal and tangible benefits within our platform, these NFTs represent a unique blend of art, utility, and gaming enhancement.

Additional details on the [Ebisu's Bay Blog](https://blog.ebisusbay.com/announcing-the-wooden-wyrm-welcoming-a-ryoshi-tales-exclusive-drop-2a4e3e83e11c)
